{"tid":1460964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真，政府比咁大隻牌我地上，你班人都唔識用，仲話要贏","createTime":"2019-08-13T05:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T06:32:11.000Z","uid":120377,"like":45,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e61d05b9b18374a05f16955973e888903eadf9","tid":1460964,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:36:38.000Z","msg":"811係有好多事發生，每件事都要值得放大<br />\n<br />\n但最重要係咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警扮示威者呀屌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解有暴力示威？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警扮示威者做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解有人掉磚？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警扮示威者做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解有人放火？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警扮示威者做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n邊個煽動暴力？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警扮示威者做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但有無人講呀？得小數文宣講，其他人唔會知<br />\n<br />\n而家佢個focus係暴力令經濟差，只要大家知道個真相係黑警同林鄭搞到經濟差，政府有咩方法唔讓步？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢樣野同個女仔同樣重要，要廣傳，要比返真相全世界知！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即刻做大量文宣呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你話我同前線割𥱊，影響軍心？呢d對外既文宣如果自己人都相信，你地就唔好講兄弟爬山同不割𥱊不分化，因為你地根本唔信自己人。"},{"pid":"66373235040ebc4d58ca8840056450e89a158663","tid":1460964,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a8fff669c1d1ecff8f5778cc215439b6e662a13","tid":1460964,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:37:45.000Z","msg":"推啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c93ba8de86e2ff501f3d16383ab6d9a28bb62e0","tid":1460964,"uid":